                    Schedule appointments with experienced doctors effortlessly.
                    Your health is our priority – book your next visit in just a few clicks.
                </p>

                <div class="hero-cta-group">
                    <button class="btn-primary js-appointment-btn">Make An Appointment</button>
                    <button class="btn-outline js-book-btn">Book Now</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="hero-right">
