                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">⚡</div>
                    <div class="feature-title">Instant Confirmation</div>
                    <div class="feature-text">
                        Get immediate confirmation and view all your upcoming visits in one place.
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">🔔</div>
                    <div class="feature-title">Smart Reminders</div>
                    <div class="feature-text">
                        Receive automatic reminders so you never miss an important consultation.
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">👨‍⚕️</div>
                    <div class="feature-title">Qualified Doctors</div>
                    <div class="feature-text">
                        Connect with experienced specialists across multiple departments and services.
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">💳</div>
                    <div class="feature-title">Secure Payments</div>
                    <div class="feature-text">
                        Pay safely using digital methods like mobile banking and online gateways.
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">📱</div>
                    <div class="feature-title">24/7 Access</div>
                    <div class="feature-text">
                        Manage your profile and appointments anytime from desktop, tablet, or mobile.
                    </div>
                </div>
